---
import VantageLayout from '../../../layouts/VantageLayout.astro';
import { brand } from '../../../data/vantage';
---

<VantageLayout title="Medical Weight Loss — VANTAGE Men's Health" description="Structured medical weight management with labs, GLP-1 evaluation, body composition support, and provider oversight.">

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="vt-sec vt-sec--ink mwl-hero">
	<div class="vt-contain">
		<p class="vt-eye">Medical Weight Loss</p>
		<h1>Weight management guided by labs, not willpower alone.</h1>
		<p class="vt-sub">Stubborn weight gain — especially around the midsection — can be driven by hormonal, metabolic, or inflammatory factors. A proper evaluation can help identify what's working against you.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--bronze" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--outline" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Beyond willpower -->
<section class="vt-sec vt-sec--graphite">
	<div class="vt-contain mwl-beyond">
		<div class="mwl-beyond__text">
			<p class="vt-eye">Beyond Willpower</p>
			<h2>Why diets fail when your biology is working against you</h2>
			<p class="vt-sub">Most men who struggle with weight have already tried calorie restriction and exercise. When results plateau or reverse, the issue is often metabolic — not motivational.</p>
			<p class="mwl-body">Low testosterone, insulin resistance, elevated cortisol, thyroid dysfunction, and poor sleep can all create a metabolic environment where fat storage is favored over fat loss. Medical weight management addresses these underlying factors.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-beyond__factors">
			<div class="vt-panel">
				<div class="vt-panel__head"><span>Contributing Factors</span><span>Metabolic</span></div>
				<div class="vt-panel__body" style="padding:0;">
					<div class="mwl-factor">
						<div class="mwl-factor__row">
							<span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>
							<h3>Hormonal imbalance</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Low testosterone promotes visceral fat storage and reduces lean muscle mass.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mwl-factor">
						<div class="mwl-factor__row">
							<span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>
							<h3>Insulin resistance</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Elevated insulin levels can make it nearly impossible to mobilize stored body fat.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mwl-factor">
						<div class="mwl-factor__row">
							<span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>
							<h3>Inflammation</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Chronic low-grade inflammation can disrupt hunger signaling and metabolic function.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mwl-factor mwl-factor--last">
						<div class="mwl-factor__row">
							<span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>
							<h3>Sleep & stress</h3>
						</div>
						<p>Cortisol dysregulation and poor sleep compound metabolic dysfunction.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Pathway timeline -->
<section class="vt-sec vt-sec--steel">
	<div class="vt-contain">
		<p class="vt-eye">Your Pathway</p>
		<h2>A structured approach to medical weight management</h2>
		<div class="mwl-pathway">
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">01</span>
				<h3>Comprehensive metabolic assessment</h3>
				<p>Labs including fasting insulin, HbA1c, thyroid, hormones, and inflammatory markers to map your metabolic baseline.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">02</span>
				<h3>Provider consultation</h3>
				<p>Review results, identify metabolic roadblocks, and discuss treatment options — including GLP-1 eligibility.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">03</span>
				<h3>Personalized protocol</h3>
				<p>A treatment plan addressing your specific metabolic factors — may include medication, hormone optimization, or both.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step mwl-pathway__step--last">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__num">04</span>
				<h3>Regular monitoring & adjustment</h3>
				<p>Ongoing lab checks, body composition tracking, and protocol refinements to sustain progress.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- GLP-1 info -->
<section class="vt-sec vt-sec--graphite">
	<div class="vt-contain mwl-glp1">
		<div class="mwl-glp1__text">
			<p class="vt-eye">GLP-1 Medications</p>
			<h2>GLP-1 receptor agonists: evaluation & oversight</h2>
			<p class="mwl-body">GLP-1 medications (such as semaglutide and tirzepatide) may be appropriate for men who meet specific clinical criteria. At VANTAGE, eligibility is determined through labs and provider evaluation — not self-selection.</p>
			<p class="mwl-body">These medications can support significant weight reduction when combined with metabolic optimization and provider oversight. They are not prescribed without proper evaluation, and ongoing monitoring is required.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-glp1__details">
			<div class="vt-panel">
				<div class="vt-panel__head"><span>Candidacy</span><span>Evaluation Required</span></div>
				<div class="vt-panel__body">
					<h3>Who may be a candidate</h3>
					<ul class="mwl-list">
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>BMI ≥ 30, or ≥ 27 with metabolic comorbidities</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Prior failed attempts with diet and exercise alone</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Lab-confirmed metabolic dysfunction</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>No contraindications identified on evaluation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="vt-panel">
				<div class="vt-panel__head"><span>Oversight</span><span>Ongoing</span></div>
				<div class="vt-panel__body">
					<h3>What's included in oversight</h3>
					<ul class="mwl-list">
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Dose titration guided by response and tolerability</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Regular lab monitoring (metabolic + hormonal panels)</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Provider check-ins at each dose adjustment</li>
						<li><span class="vt-dot vt-dot--bronze"></span>Lean mass preservation strategies</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="vt-sec vt-sec--steel">
	<div class="vt-contain">
		<div class="mwl-cta">
			<p class="vt-eye">Get Started</p>
			<h2>Ready to understand what's driving your weight?</h2>
			<p class="vt-sub">A metabolic evaluation can reveal factors that willpower alone cannot overcome. Start with an assessment.</p>
			<div class="vt-btn-row" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
				<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--bronze" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
				<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--outline" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Disclaimer -->
<div class="vt-sec--ink" style="padding:0 0 2rem;">
	<div class="vt-contain">
		<p class="mwl-disc">{brand.disclaimer}</p>
	</div>
</div>

</VantageLayout>

<style>
/* ─── Hero ─── */
.mwl-hero { padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
.mwl-hero h1 { max-width: 700px; }
.mwl-hero .vt-sub { max-width: 560px; }

/* ─── Beyond Willpower — split with data panel ─── */
.mwl-beyond { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
.mwl-body { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,237,226,0.4); line-height: 1.55; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
.mwl-beyond__factors { margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-factor { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vt-border); }
.mwl-factor--last { border-bottom: none; }
.mwl-factor__row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
.mwl-factor h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--vt-bone); margin-bottom: 0; }
.mwl-factor p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,237,226,0.4); line-height: 1.55; padding-left: 0.9rem; }

/* ─── Pathway — horizontal connected-step track ─── */
.mwl-pathway { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-top: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--vt-border); border-radius: var(--vt-r); overflow: hidden; }
.mwl-pathway__step { flex: 1; padding: 1.25rem 1rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--vt-border); }
.mwl-pathway__step--last { border-right: none; }
.mwl-pathway__num { display: block; font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--vt-bronze); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.mwl-pathway__step h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--vt-bone); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.mwl-pathway__step p { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(244,237,226,0.4); line-height: 1.5; }

/* ─── GLP-1 — split with bordered panels ─── */
.mwl-glp1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
.mwl-glp1__details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
.mwl-glp1__details h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--vt-bone); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-list li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(244,237,226,0.4); line-height: 1.55; }

/* ─── CTA — left-aligned ─── */
.mwl-cta { max-width: 560px; }
.mwl-cta .vt-sub { margin-bottom: 0; }

/* ─── Disclaimer ─── */
.mwl-disc { font-size: 0.58rem; color: rgba(244,237,226,0.15); font-style: italic; max-width: 560px; }

/* ─── Responsive ─── */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
	.mwl-beyond { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	.mwl-pathway { flex-direction: column; }
	.mwl-pathway__step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vt-border); }
	.mwl-pathway__step--last { border-bottom: none; }
	.mwl-glp1 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
